public abstract class AbstractDojo
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Widget
implements HasDojo

This abstract class aims to d'implement the necessaries method to integrate easily a Dojo widget in a GWT Widget. To do this, the class implements the interface HasDojo There are 3 points to know for implementing correctly this class :

  • How to create the Dojo widget ?
  • Do we do something after that the scripts JavaScript are loaded for the Dojo widget ?
  • Know the name of the Dojo widget to create.
This abstract class permits to call methods at " the good times" in order to avoid some memory leak problems and assume that scripts JavaScript Dojo are well loaded by the browser and they are load only once.

Author:
Vianney
